{"id":140888,"type":1,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/20/15/140888_1Bbuo.jpg","summary":"《学级王山崎》（日文：学级王ヤマザキ）是日本漫画家㭴本学原作的搞笑漫画。在1995年9月号到2001年2月号的《快乐快乐月刊》杂志上连载，全12卷。也曾改编为电视动画和电视游戏。\r\n\r\n继承山崎家的山崎以成为学级王为目标，转学到冠町的冠学园6年3班。同学、教师、山崎家的家人们被山崎引起的骚动卷入的搞笑漫画。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>学级王山崎</li><li><span>册数: </span>12</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/18930\">樫本学ヴ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span>小学馆、<a href=\"/person/8298\">青文出版社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/10206\">月刊コロコロコミック</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>学级王</li><li><span>其他出版社: </span>青文出版社</li><li><span>连载期间: </span>1995－2001</li>","collection":{"collect":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"搞笑漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":18930,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/21/86/18930_prsn_98005.jpg","name":"㭴本学","desc":"作者"},{"id":8298,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/40/d2/8298_prsn_1z141.jpg","name":"青文出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":10206,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c5/cb/10206_prsn_7PFRu.jpg","name":"月刊コロコロコミック","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":140881,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/a6/40/140881_jp.jpg"},{"id":140884,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/fb/f1/140884_jp.jpg"},{"id":140886,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/a4/c6/140886_jp.jpg"},{"id":140889,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/92/64/140889_jp.jpg"},{"id":140891,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/17/99/140891_jp.jpg"},{"id":140885,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":140890,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6d/c9/140890_jp.jpg"},{"id":140893,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/48/a8/140893_jp.jpg"},{"id":140887,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (9)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f3/ac/140887_jp.jpg"},{"id":140892,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (10)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":140883,"name":"学級王ヤマザキ (11)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9b/f7/140883_jp.jpg"},{"i